Conference fees
---------------

The seminar fee is planned to be 3 500 SKK (students, including PhD ones, 1 500
SKK) or the equivalent in euros according to the actual exchange rate (for
exchange rates, please see http://www.nbs.sk). The fee will cover the
costs of one copy of the proceedings, coffee break refreshment, breakfasts,
lunches, social event and organizing costs. Please note that accommodation and
evening meals are not included (except for the pre-paid banquet).  The
conference fee should be paid before June 30th, 2007. After this date the
conference fee is 50% higher.

